title: Stocks to Watch: Talking Markets with Liz Ann Sonders
description: Barron's senior managing editor Lauren R. Rublin, deputy editor Ben Levisohn and Liz Ann Sonders, chief investment strategist at Charles Schwab discuss the outlook for financial markets, industry sectors, and individual stocks.
